A4.text: The British Dental Association (BDA) is a registered trade union for dentists in the United Kingdom.

A5.text: The majority of the BDA's 16,000 members include high street dentists, working in general practice providing both National Health Service (NHS) and private care, and those working in community and hospital settings, universities and the British armed forces.
